Вакансія від 20 березня 2020
PHP Developer (eCommerce Department)
Gameloft
IT;
250–1000 співробітників
Харків
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
Job DescriptionWe are looking for a keen PHP Developer to join our international eCommerce team of the worldwide known video game developer and publisher. You will be working among the professionals to develop and maintain mobile shops where we sell our games.Responsibilities:
Development and support of mobile sites and billing systems according to specifications and respecting the internal rules and best practices.
Commit and follow up on the planning, reporting possible delays and proposing mitigation plans.
Submit clean code that will pass QA tests without major bugs.
Collaboration with various teams across the company in order to gather knowledge and address technical and design requirements;
Suggest solutions to improve the systems.
QualificationsTechnical requirements:
Knowledge of object-oriented development with PHP 7
Understanding of MVC and popular software design patterns
Basic front-end skills, knowledge of JavaScript, HTML and CSS
Knowledge of relational databases, MySQL in particular
Experience with source code management systems such as Git or Subversion
Pre-Intermediate level of English (ability to read/understand technical documentation and communicate in a written form is a must)
Would be a plus:
Knowledge of NoSQL databases, Redis in particular
Experience of implementing responsive web based designs
Personality traits:
Independent and with a can-do, solution oriented attitude
Good logic and analytical skills
Ability to deal with routine tasks
Ability to sustain quality work under pressure
Benefits:
Join a leading global mobile and video games publisher and developer utilizing the state-of-art mobile technologies and devices;
Become a part of the talented international team in a friendly, creative and dynamic environment;
Become a true pro in the fast-growing, exciting and innovative video games industry;
Be proud to deliver the prestigious products winning the top rankings worldwide;
Enjoy the exiting life of Gameloft with corporate trips, sponsored team building and other joyful events;
Build up your career with dynamic promotions and world wide opportunities.
